 Galvatron stopped. "You know what.....the hell with this. If we cant have 
her no one can." he was right behind the carried cat. He placed a bomb righ 
inside her left leg. He went straight down and it blew after 3 seconds. he 
didnt stay to see the damage. he flew off towards the base. he looked at 
Darkmouse."This wa s alost mission. We will have to train in the simulation 
chmaber before next time."

--part1_16.115abd42.28b9de2a_boundary
